summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5417 for the improvement of 57th Avenue South, from a point 100 feet south of Bangor Street to Ryan Street, by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 67575, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
